{"tid":293444,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［開箱］ LG 27ud69 4K Moon","createTime":"2017-06-22T07:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T10:15:22.000Z","uid":44035,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51ce524f2cbcbf64a9ea55f00916939a54cf1cd5","tid":293444,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"第一次係度開開箱post，希望大家滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁今次呢隻moon就係腦場某知名鋪頭訂貨（呢隻野應該唔會有現貨，除非條友呃9我）<br />\n<br />\n我星期六訂貨，星期三已經有得拎，十分快手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但有樣野要屌屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，佢facebook寫自己九點關門，我琴日八點半去琴已經拉左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁惟有今日再拎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終，今日終於不負眾望，成功帶走左佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153230_3a8482512792939f565210fc3fa47639.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153230_3a8482512792939f565210fc3fa47639.jpg&h=61eed5c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153248_4d18f8f71f616cce4e1ba5299be6118f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153248_4d18f8f71f616cce4e1ba5299be6118f.jpg&h=e3feff61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153250_145605a1cc616a8a93d3e46bc074e91b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153250_145605a1cc616a8a93d3e46bc074e91b.jpg&h=fff98172&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153253_6431851c030afa60beaeda57aa6be763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153253_6431851c030afa60beaeda57aa6be763.jpg&h=4c4a6f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n背隻相有某公司名...因為我當場開左黎check機，不是打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一次唔敢打太長，開箱會係下面講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cecba00f53076f794fa3f2a3557199f8d6b6f8","tid":293444,"uid":12124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"阻人收工死家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5ad1a85c79084e2bc7273e42a343795f88131b","tid":293444,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"39b90c7ee097722401da3fbc5e0921fb5d69278c","tid":293444,"uid":12124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阻人收工死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f3918090af40bf36e58a2faef948425e520a7328","tid":293444,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"繼續講開箱！我諗大家都係想睇相多過我講架喇，去相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153550_1086a768db16d5e6f7a6b05d138056c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153550_1086a768db16d5e6f7a6b05d138056c5.jpg&h=6cbc4ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153553_54ba33169bd5ae29182cc6e7a8aaf87c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153553_54ba33169bd5ae29182cc6e7a8aaf87c.jpg&h=5cd62bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153557_7ea2bb2128b88b10dc4b1b46c198a7b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153557_7ea2bb2128b88b10dc4b1b46c198a7b3.jpg&h=e9e723dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153559_ee6ae265982ae36e9b10508487624ab1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153559_ee6ae265982ae36e9b10508487624ab1.jpg&h=d3e00f7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153601_b40634f51c24fcf0fa63d76efa57224a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153601_b40634f51c24fcf0fa63d76efa57224a.jpg&h=68bfe216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n配件都十分齊全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153652_c50de1607f577a2417012dca59d323b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153652_c50de1607f577a2417012dca59d323b1.jpg&h=f871673d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153654_7f6aa9d4524f2f1d3d3111f16fc8cc77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153654_7f6aa9d4524f2f1d3d3111f16fc8cc77.jpg&h=5acf4c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩樣當黃豆就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153733_40c6a07d94d1ab31eedc4bc9bdc2f6d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F153733_40c6a07d94d1ab31eedc4bc9bdc2f6d3.jpg&h=723aecd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個箱有教你點整個架，都幾貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我認為有正常智力既人自己研究一分鐘都應該識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到真身部份 相信大家等左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/153941_249d88eaff7e7b3