normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁附送多兩張遊戲圖，之後我會再貼下高畫質game既實戰圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/154454_7f1b117c75faae330a915c6bee1997e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F154454_7f1b117c75faae330a915c6bee1997e6.jpg&h=de4fccce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/22/154501_ac45b14ae79a18bf62bf8c8f56f6490c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F154501_ac45b14ae79a18bf62bf8c8f56f6490c.jpg&h=6d69649c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01e1e8fe9a864d78cbffc19795273c889bce264b","tid":293444,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"感想部分<br />\n<br />\n隻moon黎講都十分高質，冇光點死點問題，算係完美quality，冇不滿啦，盛惠hkd4390。<br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝多鮫魚巴打開既moon知識post，實在獲益良多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1a16acb377e9752d62d9fdbe8f3ad492f19ad2","tid":293444,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:07:23.000Z","msg":"邊間買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪可以試哂0死點0光點"},{"pid":"f67ddaf77d7726e4c3dbfd673bc312cbcb785a9b","tid":293444,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"有無HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc30366302a1602e28d0781090416b947c6216e6","tid":293444,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無HDR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nNo"},{"pid":"1721f76c871ab4fe978774df64b844f064d9a97c","tid":293444,"uid":44035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,